snippet.title: Thrifty Business Season 4 #25 EcomChicago Recap with The Unlikely Entrepreneur Robyn Johnson
snippet.description: EcomChicago was last week and Jay had a great time. One of the segments of Ecom was a panel called The Titans Of Ecommerce. The panel was Jay, Chris Green & Robyn Johnson. Robyn is know as The Unlikely Entrepreneur. Robyn Johnson started with just $100 and grew that into a seven figure business. She has taken her nerdy passion of selling on Amazon and become an expert on teaching others How To. Jay and Robyn will recap the event and Jay will talk to Robyn how she got from investing $100 to being a Titan Of Ecommerce. Jay's cohost is the always happy and effervescent , Margaret Collier aka Texas Gal Treasures.
